<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
    <title>邀请有礼奖励规则</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base/BH_base.css">
    <style>
        html,body{
            margin:0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width:768px;
            height: auto;
            background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ff5531 0%, #ffb640 30%);
            background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%,#ff5531), color-stop(30%,#ffb640));
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ff5531 0%,#ffb640 30%);
            background: -o-linear-gradient(top, #ff5531 0%,#ffb640 30%);
            background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #ff5531 0%,#ffb640 30%);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff5531 0%,#ffb640 30%);
        }
        .invite-rule-page{
            width: 100%;
        }
        .rule-main1{margin-bottom: 0.34rem;}
        img{width: 100%;}
        .main1-cont1{
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            background: url("/img/invite/rule/main1_top.png") center no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% 100%;
        }
        .main1-cont1-list,.main1-cont2,.main2-cont{
            margin:0 auto;
            width:6.92rem;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .main1-cont1-list{
            padding-top: 0.24rem;
            border-radius: 0.1rem 0.1rem 0 0;
        }
        .main1-cont2{
            padding-bottom:0.28rem;
            border-radius: 0 0 0.1rem 0.1rem;
        }
        .main1-cont2-table{
            margin:0 auto;
            width: 6rem;
        }
        .main1-cont2-list{width: 100%;}
        .txt-item{
            padding:0 0.31rem;
            line-height: 0.36rem;
            font-size: 0.24rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .mb38{margin-bottom: 0.38rem;}


        .title2{
            margin:0 auto;
            width:2.52rem;
        }
        .main2-cont{
            margin-top:0.2rem;
            padding:0.25rem 0 0.18rem;
            border-radius: 0.1rem;
        }

        .rule-bottom{
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1.66rem;
        }
        .bottom-l,.bottom-r{
            position: absolute;
        }
        .bottom-l{
            bottom:0;
            left: 0;
            width: 1.4rem;
            height: 0.8rem;
            background: url("/img/invite/rule/bottom_l.png") center no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% 100%;
        }
        .bottom-r{
            bottom: 0.06rem;
            right: 0.06rem;
            width: 2.28rem;
            height: 1.52rem;
            background: url("/img/invite/rule/bottom_r.png") center no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="invite-rule-page">
        <div class="rule-main1">
            <img src="/img/invite/rule/title1.png" alt="" class="title1">
            <div class="main1-cont">
                <div class="main1-cont1">
                    <ul class="main1-cont1-list">
                        <li class="txt-item mb38">
                            1.活动期间，邀请好友注册成功并完成首次投资且单笔金额
                            ≥5000元，推荐人可获得<span style="color:#ff5431;">8元现金红包</span>；好友第二次投资且
                            单笔金额≥5000元，推荐人还可获得<span style="color:#ff5431;">5元现金红包</span>。
                        </li>
                        <li class="txt-item mb38">
                            2.邀请单个好友可得现金红包两个封顶，在完成规定要求的
                            投资后，由系统自动发放至您的铂恒金服账户中，您可在
                            【我的账户】-【我的红包】中查看；
                        </li>
                        <li class="txt-item">
                            3.每人可邀请好友人数不设上限，邀请人数越多，推广奖励
                            越多；奖励规则如下：
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="main1-cont2">
                    <div class="main1-cont2-table">
                        <img src="/img/invite/rule/main1_table.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <ul class="main1-cont2-list">
                        <li class="txt-item mb38">
                            4.满足条件后须找在线客服登记，现金红包将在5个工作日
                            内发放至您的铂恒金服账户中。
                        </li>
                        <li class="txt-item">
                            5.本活动最终解释权归铂恒金服所有，如有任何疑问请致电
                            客服热线<span style="color:#ff5431;">400-1888-686</span>。
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-main2">
            <div class="title2">
                <img src="/img/invite/rule/title2.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <ul class="main2-cont">
                <li class="txt-item mb38">
                    1.好友注册时，请他/她在<span style="color:#ff5431;">"推荐人"</span>一栏填写您的邀请码。
                </li>
                <li class="txt-item">
                    2.直接分享您的推荐链接来邀请好友注册。(邀请码、邀请
                    链接请在“我的账户”--“邀请有礼”中查询)。
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-bottom">
            <div class="bottom-l"></div>
            <div class="bottom-r"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>